title: 210. Words & Nerds 3rd Birthday Party with SPECIAL GUESTS
itunes:author: Words and Nerds: Authors, books and literature.
itunes:summary:
Join HOSTS Adrian Beck, Jack Heath & Dani Vee as we celebrate 3 years of Words and Nerds Podcast.

We found 9 of the most fun humans who were keen to celebrate in Zoom style. Join Felice Arena, Matt Cosgrove, Nat Amoore, Sue Whiting, Alex Miles, Mick Elliott, Jules Faber, Nicole Hayes and Tristan Bancks for some mayhem.

Watch the video on the W&N FB page.
